this feeling. All in all it was a pretty good performance.\"</p> </div> </div> <div id=\"block-52e24bf1e4b021712daf2dda\" class=\"block is-key-event\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-01-24T11:21:21.813Z\">11.21am <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <h2 class=\"block-title\">England win by 57 runs</h2> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <p>Whisper it, but that was a bit of a hammering. Yes, it's academic in the grand scheme of things. And yes, it was a bit of an Australian second string. But after this tour any crumb of comfort is to be cherished. And celebrated disproportionately.&nbsp;</p> </div> </div> <div id=\"block-52e24b90e4b021712daf2dd8\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-01-24T11:17:21.577Z\">11.17am <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <h2 class=\"block-title\">England fans: may I suggest this …</h2> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <figure class=\"element element-video\" data-canonical-url=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3GwjfUFyY6M\"                                                                                > <iframe width=\"460\" height=\"345\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/3GwjfUFyY6M?wmode=opaque&feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe> <figcaption>Celebrate good times, come on</figcaption> </figure> <p>Australia fans may also enjoy that. Seeing as it's 3-1 and all.</p> </div> </div> <div id=\"block-52e24a33e4b021712daf2dd6\" class=\"block is-key-event\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-01-24T11:16:18.564Z\">11.16am <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <h2 class=\"block-title\">WICKET!!!! ENGLAND WIN! Pattinson c Buttler b Bresnan 4 (Australia 259 all out)</h2> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <p>England have beaten Australia! Repeat: England have beaten Australia!</p> </div> </div> <div id=\"block-52e24883e4b021712daf2dd3\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time date